<subSubSection lastPageId="24" lastPageNumber="41" pageId="23" pageNumber="40" type="type species">
<paragraph pageId="23" pageNumber="40">Type species.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="23" pageNumber="40">
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Brasilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="morretesi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="40">Brasilaxia morretesi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Théry">Thery</normalizedToken>
, 1935 by original designation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="24" pageNumber="41">
<pageBreakToken pageId="24" pageNumber="41" start="start">The</pageBreakToken>
monotypic genus lacks taxonomic problems. The type species was synonymised with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1913" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="costifera">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Anthaxia costifera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Obenberger, 1913 by 
<bibRefCitation author="Cobos, A" journalOrPublisher="Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria)" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="103 - 165" refId="B19" refString="Cobos, A, 1956. Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria) 5: 103 - 165" title="Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Primera parte: Subgeneros Cylindrophora Sol. y Paracuris Obenb." volume="5" year="1956">Cobos (1956)</bibRefCitation>
. A further two species described in the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thery" authorityYear="1935" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Brasilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Brasilaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1958" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Brasilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jacobi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Brasilaxia jacobi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Obenberger, 1958 and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1958" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Brasilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="olavei">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Brasilaxia olavei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Obenberger, 1958) were removed from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thery" authorityYear="1935" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Brasilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Brasilaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and synonymised by 
<bibRefCitation author="Cobos, A" journalOrPublisher="Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria)" pageId="28" pageNumber="45" pagination="5 - 235" refId="B21" refString="Cobos, A, 1972. Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Tercera parte: Subgenero Agrilaxia Kerremans. Archivos de Instituto de Aclimatacion (Almeria) 16: 5 - 235" title="Ensayo monografico sobre las Anthaxia Eschs. (Coleoptera, Buprestidae) de America. Tercera parte: Subgenero Agrilaxia Kerremans." volume="16" year="1972">Cobos (1972)</bibRefCitation>
with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cobos" authorityYear="1956" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mariae" subGenus="Cylindrophora">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Anthaxia (Cylindrophora) mariae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1958" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Brasilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jacobi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Brasilaxia jacobi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) - see above, and with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Germain &amp; Kerremans" authorityYear="1906" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Curis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="oyarcei">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Curis oyarcei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Germain &amp; Kerremans, 1906 (
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1958" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Brasilaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="olavei">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Brasilaxia olavei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
-currently 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Germain &amp; Kerremans" baseAuthorityYear="1906" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Ctenoderus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="oyarcei">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="41">Ctenoderus oyarcei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Holynski" authorityYear="1988" lsidName="" pageId="24" pageNumber="41" rank="tribe" tribe="Curidini">Curidini</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
